TradingBot Live Dashboard 
==========================
REAL_TRADING_ENABLED = False in base_config file

Strategy 1 → 2 Green candles → Buy → Profit/Loss Exit
Strategy 2 → 3 Green candles → Buy → Profit/Loss Exit
Strategy 3 -> EMA Crossover -> Buy → Profit/Loss Exit
______________________________________________________


QUICK START (after clone)
--------------------------
1. Run setup (installs deps, creates .env files):
   bash setup.sh

2. Edit credentials:
   nano shared/.env
   → Fill in: KITE_API_KEY, KITE_API_SECRET, DB_PASSWORD

3. Start everything:
   bash run_live_dashboard.sh

4. Open browser:
   http://<your-server-ip>:5173

5. In dashboard → click "Setup DB" to create MySQL tables


STOP
----
   bash stop_live_dashboard.sh


LOGS
----
   tail -f logs/api.log    # FastAPI backend
   tail -f logs/vite.log   # Vite frontend


MANUAL START (without script)
------------------------------
   # Backend
   uvicorn api:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --reload

   # Frontend
   cd dashboard-ui && npm run dev


REQUIREMENTS
------------
   Python: pip install -r shared/setup_system/requirements.txt
   Node:   cd dashboard-ui && npm install
   MySQL:  running on localhost


PORTS
-----
   8000 → FastAPI backend (internal only, proxied by Vite)
   5173 → Vite frontend  (open this in browser)
